    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_7884890275308725349.png",
                "id": "talent87951",
                "key": "西風劍術·宗室",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "西風劍術·宗室"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素傷害</span>，如果本角色未附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冷酷之心</span>，則使其附屬<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冷酷之心</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冷酷之心</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附屬角色使用冰潮的渦旋時：</span>移除此狀態，使本次傷害+2。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/78b526224710dda639b49972145339a9_465663028092066680.png",
                "id": "talent16958",
                "key": "冰潮的渦旋",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰潮的渦旋"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成2點<span style=\"color: #99FFFF\">冰元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">光降之劍</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/72b7716be67efac4ec94efde16957180_1210300734486241949.png",
                "id": "talent13815",
                "key": "凝浪之光劍",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "凝浪之光劍"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">優菈使用「普通攻擊」或「元素戰技」時：</span>此牌累積2點「能量層數」，但是優菈不會獲得充能。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">結束階段：</span>棄置此牌，造成3點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span>；每有1點「能量層數」，都使此傷害+1.</p><p>（影響此牌「<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span>」的效果會生效於「<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">能量層數</span>」。）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_5003450486270982836.png",
                "id": "talent4145",
                "key": "光降之劍",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/3f07051befd3fcb50000df92021710d6_2066808595207023167.png",
                "title": "光降之劍"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超導</span>：本傷害+1，對目標以外的所有敵方角色造成1點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透傷害</span></p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">凍結</span>：本傷害+1，使目標本回合無法行動（受到<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>傷害后提前解除，但是傷害+2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_6199934901455496656.png",
                "id": "talent27319",
                "key": "冰元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理傷害</span></strong></p><p>物理傷害不會附著元素，也不會發生元素反應。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗一層可用次數；</p><p>可用次數耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/25/84496276/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_5625012468697809449.png",
